---
title: Song List
layout: layout
---

<p class="lead">This is a collection of songs we learn and play together at our meet ups.</p>

<p>A playlist of these songs is available on <a href="https://open.spotify.com/user/spilth/playlist/1NaTfvTr9vGRuLPFZ5vPPz">Spotify</a> and <a href="https://www.ultimate-guitar.com/user/playlist/shared?h=CZXbBj5q2-w1AMYO_MpRLFrg">Ultimate Guitar</a>. You can also <a href="/pdfs/songbook.pdf">download a PDF book of all the songs</a>.</p>

<p><a href="/pdfs/songbook.pdf" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-download fa-fw"></i> Download Songbook </a></p>

<table class="table table-hover">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Title</th>
      <th>Artist</th>
      <th><span class="d-none d-md-inline">Download</span> <i class="d-md-none fas fa-file-pdf fa-fw"></i></th>
      <th><span class="d-none d-md-inline">Listen</span> <i class="d-md-none fab fa-spotify fa-fw"></i></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <% data.songs.sort_by(&:title).each do |song| %>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <% if song.chordpro %>
          <%= link_to song.title, "/songs/#{song.chordpro}" %>
        <% else %>
          <%= link_to song.title,  "/pdfs/#{song.chordpro}.pdf" %>
        <% end %>
      </td>
      <td><%= song.artist %></td>
      <td>
        <% if song.chordpro %>
          <% link_to  "/pdfs/#{song.chordpro}.pdf" do %>
            <span class="d-none d-md-inline">Download</span>
            <i class="d-md-none fas fa-file-pdf fa-fw"></i>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </td>
      <td>
        <% if song.spotify %>
          <% link_to song.spotify do %>
            <span class="d-none d-md-inline">Listen</span>
            <i class="d-md-none fab fa-spotify fa-fw"></i>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>
